<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br><br>最近啊，我回答的不是连带问题被删，就是审核折叠。<br><br>但我依然充满斗志、积极乐观。<br>因为我有这些治愈的微笑：<br><br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1aab4eeba81bd8070a87e80a098a6ee0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="518" data-rawheight="344" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="518" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1aab4eeba81bd8070a87e80a098a6ee0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="518" data-rawheight="344" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="518" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1aab4eeba81bd8070a87e80a098a6ee0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1aab4eeba81bd8070a87e80a098a6ee0_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bb2571b7c2e6cbeffae0cb372f026fa7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="576" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="576" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bb2571b7c2e6cbeffae0cb372f026fa7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="576" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="576" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bb2571b7c2e6cbeffae0cb372f026fa7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/bb2571b7c2e6cbeffae0cb372f026fa7_b.jpg">


